like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T20:29:08.000Z","msg":"會唔會太急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁玩完仲攰過返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:39:48.000Z","msg":"有冇咩建議可以cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:55:28.000Z","msg":"我黎緊都去北海道 8日都留北海道<br />\n如果一定要去名古屋<br />\n咁函館會唔會考慮唔去住？ 登別值得留一晚玩下浸下溫泉 反而洞庭湖無乜野睇<br />\n不過個個人嘅意見都唔同 有人鐘意玩多啲地方睇多啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c07bf4f5fdef130cda4be7c24b40bfd8bdd388","tid":1728282,"uid":139972,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:08:37.000Z","msg":"北海道2月，好早日落<br />\nAnd隨時有風雪，你坐JR<br />\n有心理準備好啲"},{"pid":"f40554222aaaf06be2490e8a5436b95ba1986f0d","tid":1728282,"uid":53182,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:35:39.000Z","msg":"覺得你太趕 特別係旭川果一日 都唔知你去得邊 <br />\n富良野點到點旭川都要時間 加上考慮暴雪問題 有d難度<br />\n如果單純想睇青池&amp;動物園 買tour好過啦"},{"pid":"cb0b15beea53e7cda423fc76cec57b3309b5001a","tid":1728282,"uid":80512,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:45:19.000Z","msg":"見親北海道post都同一個通病，太貪心<br />\n你問會唔會太密？比足九日你去講果啲地方都勁趕啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇睇地圖同埋啲人寫遊記先<br />\n<br />\n你個行程一係skip名古屋<br />\n唔skip名古屋就skip函館<br />\n唔肯skip函館就skip洞爺/登別是但一度<br />\n<br />\n因為你個Day4完全唔知你想點，上登別溫泉街本身仲要搭轉巴士，4個鐘你做到啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要話去完札幌再去小樽跟住又天狗山雪橇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋北海道2月三點幾已經天黑<br />\n<br />\nDay 5當你去旭川去完個動物園都天黑返札幌啦仲諗富良野，富良野2月無乜地方岩去"},{"pid":"0c376375c9421b1021a00db342936227477c1806","tid":1728282,"uid":82243,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T20:12:33.000Z","msg":"前兩日喺Asia Miles換左2張1月中既CTS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二次去<br />\n有冇深度遊介紹"},{"pid":"88c9cba957fb84868feb04c856ce35cf1acff505","tid":1728282,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8c776c44218da373f3d33316b36bca1acdef921","tid":1728282,"uid":139100,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6398cbc8296e6c8b4d4f74c178e817a735c31afe","tid":1728282,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9497f480eaa77d5a34fb7302d0f93e03b417e42b","tid":1728282,"uid":42130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T07:17:40.000Z","msg":"Skip jor 名古屋<br />\n9日玩晒北海道<br />\n<br />\n如果未book機票"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:40:18.000Z","msg":"cannot skip，因為札幌函館都冇機返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:22:03.000Z","msg":"玩到第八日函館飛返名古屋 <br />\n咁當初點解揀名古屋返香港？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"純碎諗住如果要東京名古屋大阪是但揀一度，咁我揀名古屋未去過"},{"pid":"25374996ea3ac386dccd2016dcd4f5f982926bfa","tid":1728282,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48cfa09599d8fe354d7e14193f5e4b01369c6853","tid":1728282,"uid":169208,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d79d88ce2d24a72b19e24e5ab368308674efe0b7","tid":1728282,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9d1e787555b3cb3d277654346ed2fdbbac69e69","tid":1728282,"uid":169208,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T20:29:08.000Z","msg":"會唔會太急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁玩完仲攰過返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:39:48.000Z","msg":"有冇咩建議可以cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:55:28.000Z","msg":"我黎緊都去北海道 8日都留北海道<br />\n如果一定要去名古屋<br />\n咁函館會唔會考慮唔去住？ 登別值得留一晚玩下浸下溫泉 反而洞庭湖無乜野睇